metadata.name: Decayed Elegance
metadata.description:
Taken during a road-trip along Route 66, these abandoned vehicles stood in its full grandeur somewhere in New Mexico. Scenes such as this almost seem like a time travel, opening the window of our imaginations , taking us back in the day when these vehicles were used, their owners, their whereabouts and plenty other questions with very little answers. 

Creator: Ash Page
Location: New Mexico
Equipment: Fujifilm X100V
